==大眾評價==
[[File:Sherlock_Holmes_-_The_Man_with_the_Twisted_Lip.jpg|thumb]]創作，收錄在《[[歪嘴的人|歪嘴的人]]》一文中。]]

《福爾摩斯冒險史》系列在《{{le|河岸杂志|The Strand Magazine}}》受到好評<ref name="leeds">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/viewer/bl/0000076/18921121/094/0008 |title=Literary Arrivals |work=Leeds Mercury |page=8 |date=1892-11-21 |accessdate=2015-06-09 |subscription=true |via={{le|英国报纸档案|British Newspaper Archive}} |archive-date=2020-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200514051751/https://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/account/register?countrykey=0&showgiftvoucherclaimingoptions=false&gift=false&nextpage=%2faccount%2flogin%3freturnurl%3d%252fviewer%252fbl%252f0000076%252f18921121%252f094%252f0008&rememberme=false&cookietracking=false&partnershipkey=0&newsletter=false&offers=false&registerreason=none&showsubscriptionoptions=false&showcouponmessaging=false&showfreetrialmessaging=false&showregisteroptions=false&showloginoptions=false&isonlyupgradeable=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>，當首篇《[[波希米亞醜聞|波希米亞醜聞]]》於1891年7月出版後，《{{le|赫爾每日郵報|Hull Daily Mail}}》評價[[柯南·道爾|柯南·道爾]]是位傑出的創造性天才。<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/viewer/bl/0000323/18910714/004/0003 |title=Local Intelligence |work=Hull Daily Mail |page=3 |date=1891-07-17 |accessdate=2015-06-09 |subscription=true |via={{le|英国报纸档案|British Newspaper Archive}}}}</ref>在《福爾摩斯冒險史》系列刊登完時，《貝爾法斯特新聞報》刊登另一名《河岸杂志》的作者評論，他在那則評論評價這或許是一年前受到大量關注的作品，然而柯南·道爾獨特地寫作能力與品質之間的落差可在這系列的作品間發現。<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/viewer/bl/0000038/18920817/033/0007 |title=Literature |work=Belfast News Letter |page=7 |date=1892-08-17 |accessdate=2015-06-09 |subscription=true |via={{le|英国报纸档案|British Newspaper Archive}} |archive-date=2020-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200514051801/https://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/account/register?countrykey=0&showgiftvoucherclaimingoptions=false&gift=false&nextpage=%2faccount%2flogin%3freturnurl%3d%252fviewer%252fbl%252f0000038%252f18920817%252f033%252f0007&rememberme=false&cookietracking=false&partnershipkey=0&newsletter=false&offers=false&registerreason=none&showsubscriptionoptions=false&showcouponmessaging=false&showfreetrialmessaging=false&showregisteroptions=false&showloginoptions=false&isonlyupgradeable=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>《{{le|里兹信使报|Leeds Mercury}}》稱讚柯南·道爾利用許多怪僻及細節來點綴福爾摩斯的特徵<ref name="leeds"/>，然而《{{le|切爾滕納姆觀察者期刊|Cheltenham Looker-On}}》卻評論福爾摩斯有時候讓人感到相當沉悶，並指出在描述福爾摩斯的弱點時顯得令人生厭<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/viewer/bl/0000226/18921203/010/0017 |title=Literary Gossip |work=Cheltenham Looker-On |page=17 |date=1892-12-03 |accessdate=2015-06-09 |subscription=true |via={{le|英国报纸档案|British Newspaper Archive}} |archive-date=2020-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200514051807/https://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/account/register?countrykey=0&showgiftvoucherclaimingoptions=false&gift=false&nextpage=%2faccount%2flogin%3freturnurl%3d%252fviewer%252fbl%252f0000226%252f18921203%252f010%252f0017&rememberme=false&cookietracking=false&partnershipkey=0&newsletter=false&offers=false&registerreason=none&showsubscriptionoptions=false&showcouponmessaging=false&showfreetrialmessaging=false&showregisteroptions=false&showloginoptions=false&isonlyupgradeable=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《漢普郡電訊報》的記者則感慨地表示道爾更有思想的作品如《{{le|麥卡·克拉克|Micah Clarke}}》並沒有像福爾摩斯系列受到歡迎，同時總結當一位作家在撰寫文章時，也不得不為了迎合大眾喜愛而付出代價。<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/viewer/bl/0000069/18921203/006/0002 |title=Literary Notes and News |work=Hampshire Telegraph |page=2 |date=1892-12-03 |accessdate=2015-06-09 |subscription=true |via={{le|英国报纸档案|British Newspaper Archive}}}}</ref>

==改編作品==
夏洛克·福爾摩斯系列作品已多次在電影及戲劇間經歷改編，在超過200部電影中，福爾摩斯這一腳色曾由70多位{{le|飾演夏洛克·福爾摩斯角色演員列表|List of actors who have played Sherlock Holmes|演員飾演}}過。<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/6789921/Sherlock-Holmes-pipe-dreams.html |title=Sherlock Holmes: pipe dreams |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |publisher=[[Telegraph_Media_Group|Telegraph Media Group]] |location=London |last=Fox |first=Chloe |date=2009-12-15 |accessdate=2015-06-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812073358/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/6789921/Sherlock-Holmes-pipe-dreams.html |archivedate=2019-08-12 }}</ref>許多電影及電視劇都有以《夏洛克·福爾摩斯冒險史》為標題的影集，但這當中有一部分是經過改編的故事<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://explore.bfi.org.uk/4ce2b6c02773c |title=The Adventures of Sherlock Holmes (1939) |publisher=[[British_Film_Institute|British Film Institute]] |accessdate=2015-06-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823141811/https://www.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b6c02773c |archivedate=2018-08-23 }}</ref>，或是將多個道爾撰寫的故事重新組合，甚至改編原著[[四簽名|四簽名]]的情節，並冠以此標題上市。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://explore.bfi.org.uk/4ce2b6e89e25b |title=The Adventures of Sherlock Holmes (1905) |publisher=British Film Institute |accessdate=2015-06-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814232558/http://www.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b6e89e25b |archivedate=2018-08-14 }}</ref><ref name=bennett>{{cite web |language=en |author=Carl Bennett |url= http://www.silentera.com/PSFL/data/A/AdventuresOfSherlockHo1905.html |title=Adventures of Sherlock Holmes |work=The Progressive Silent Film List |year=2000|accessdate=2010-08-09 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100802060015/http://www.silentera.com/PSFL/data/A/AdventuresOfSherlockHo1905.html | archivedate= 2010-08-02| deadurl= no}}</ref>[[艾琳·艾德勒|艾琳·艾德勒]]僅在本系列的[[波希米亞醜聞|波希米亞醜聞]]出場過一次，之後就未再現身過，然而在現在的改編作品中，時常會引用她來當作重要腳色。{{sfn|Thompson|2013|pp=83–85}}通常在現代的改編中，艾琳·艾德勒被描繪成是福爾摩斯愛慕的人，例如{{le|羅伯特·達赫蒂|Robert Doherty (writer)}}的《[[福爾摩斯與華生|福爾摩斯與華生]]》，以及[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]的《[[新世紀福爾摩斯|新世紀福爾摩斯]]》<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://primetime.unrealitytv.co.uk/sherlock-spoilers-lara-pulver-says-irene-adler-will-definitely-be-back-for-new-series/ |title=Sherlock Spoilers: Lara Pulver says she has no doubt that Irene Adler will be back! |last=Howell |first=Anna |publisher=Unreality TV |date=2013-04-19 |accessdate=2015-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610130642/http://primetime.unrealitytv.co.uk/sherlock-spoilers-lara-pulver-says-irene-adler-will-definitely-be-back-for-new-series/ |archive-date=2015-06-10 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>，儘管這些改編故事在戲劇中仍聲稱福爾摩斯對艾琳·艾德勒情感並非與愛情相似。{{sfn|Thompson|2013|pp=83–85}}本系列中的許多短篇故事都被收錄在[[ITV格拉納達|ITV格拉納達]]改編系列電視劇《[[歇洛克·福爾摩斯_(1984年電視劇)|夏洛克·福爾摩斯]]》中，這系列電視劇從1984年播放至1994年。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://explore.bfi.org.uk/4ce2b9f16572d |title=Jeremy Brett |publisher=British Film Institute |accessdate=2015-06-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190711220813/https://www.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b9f16572d |archivedate=2019-07-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>[[BBC廣播四台|BBC廣播四台]]在1990年至1991年將《福爾摩斯冒險史》戲劇化，由{{le|克萊夫·梅里森|Clive Merrison}}飾演[[夏洛克·福爾摩斯|夏洛克·福爾摩斯]]，{{le|邁克爾·威廉斯|Michael Williams (actor)}}飾演[[約翰·華生|約翰·華生]]。{{le|伯特·科爾斯|Bert Coules}}是首席編劇，但故事情節編寫同時與文森特·麥克納尼（Vincent McInerny）及彼得·麥基（Peter Mackie）共同完成，導演一職則由帕特里克·瑞納（Patrick Rayner）與恩德·威廉姆斯（Enyd Williams）共同擔任。<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://merrisonholmes.com/adventures.php |title=The Adventures of Sherlock Holmes |accessdate=2016-12-12 |website=The BBC complete audio Sherlock Holmes |author=Bert Coules | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20190813173526/http://merrisonholmes.com/adventures.php | archivedate= 2019-08-13| deadurl= no }}</ref>

